<h4>New Event</h4>
				<p>Dear Players, a new week and a new event for you. It is called <strong>the Revenge of the Red Dark Knight</strong>. On Manday (May 2nd) in Lorencia at 16:00, 20:00 and 23:00 a bad and cruel Dark Knight will show up. It will be there to cause havoc on the MU continent. He also wants to destroy all heroes who wants to stop him. He will be there for an hour unless someone will be able to destroy him. Whoever will be able to do that will receive an <strong>ancient item</strong>. May this trophy be respected by the winner. </p>
				<p>Secondly, a short maintenance is necessary on the Active server so on Sunday evening it will be restarted. It will be offline for a minute. </p>
				<p class="text-right"><small>2016-04-30 14:27</small></p>
<hr>
<h4>Maintenance</h4>
				<p>A quick update from the administration. As you all know there are some connectivity issues on our server. There is a bug in the server files. However, the server files provider will have a patch ready tonight. When we have it, we will update the server files immediately.</p>
				<p>Because of that a <strong>short maintenance will be required</strong>. It should take around <strong>15 minutes</strong> to apply the patch. The server will be unavailable during that time. The patch should be available around midnight (0:00 GMT+1) so expect the downtime around that time. It will also be a good opportunity for us to <strong>apply the changes</strong> mentioned in the <strong>previous message</strong> so there won't be the downtime on April 20th.</p>
				<p>We are really sorry for the inconvenience but we hope that more players will join us really soon as a result. Don't forget about the new event!</p>
				<p class="text-right"><small>2016-04-18 20:42</small></p>
				<hr>
				<h4>Server Updates</h4>
				<p>Dear Players, on April 20th, 2016 at 19:00 GMT+1 there will be a short maintenance to be able to introduce several changes described below.</p>
				<ul>
				    <li>Every new character and every character that hasn’t been reset before will get <strong>additional 100 Level Up Points</strong>. If you have a character that you created earlier but you did not reach your first reset, you will get additional 100 points too.</li>
					<li>We will add to in-game shops items that will not ruin the economy on our server but they will be useful for new players (i.e. Bone+3+12 and equivalents).</li>
					<li>Rings level 40 and 80 will give you <strong>300,000 Zen or a jewel</strong> that will give you easy access to potions for new and low level characters. </li>
					<br>
					<li><strong>NEW EVENT</strong>: Mini Golden Dragon. From now on every Golden Invasion will also spawn a Small Golden Dragon. The best thing about it is that pretty much every character will be able to kill it. It will have a small damage and defence rate but lots of health points. It will try to survive without being able to kill anyone. If you manage to kill it, it will drop a BoK+4.</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-right"><small>2016-04-18 17:43</small></p>
