<h4>Player of the Day and Player of the Week</h4>
<p>Dear Players, it is time to start our first server event. As you can see on our website, we announce who is the <strong>Player of the Day</strong>. It is a character that is #1 in our <a href="?module=score_ranking">score ranking</a>. Starting tomorrow (11.04.2016) we will award a player of the day with a <strong>Box of Kundun +4</strong>. The Player of the Week (a player that was a player of the day the most often during a week) will get <strong>3x Box of Kundun +4</strong>. So that's worth fighting for. The rewards will be delivered to your warehouse.</p>
<p>Secondly, we would like to let you know that a <strong>scheduled maintenance</strong> will occur tomorrow (11.04.2016) at 11 pm (GMT+1) and the server will be offline for around 10 minutes. This is required to fix a few bugs including the issue with getting DC.</p>
<p class="text-right"><small>2016-04-10 20:13</small></p>
